3,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最普通做法：<br />\ngoogle merge sort</blockquote><br />\nsorry 冇睇清楚，唔洗sort<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b19211d4982eb4079e5543d7e3dc6c1fc15da61","tid":206293,"uid":61769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩新手上路自學PYTHON<br />\n上網搵到條問題想請教<br />\n<br />\nPlease write a recursive function to reverse the array.<br />\nOriginal Array = {a,b,c,d,e}<br />\nAfter passing through the function, Transformed Array = {a,b,e,d,c}<br />\n<br />\n方向應該點諗好?</blockquote><br />\nfn rev:<br />\nrev(其餘) + 第一個<br />\n<br />\n第一個就retuen 自己</blockquote><br />\n好似明明地 試試先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fcb40b0b132e4dfda3ec34c5d40fd5f195537de","tid":206293,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:55:44.000Z","msg":"dictionary 無得排order個喎"},{"pid":"e4793f7e3e9fa174744bfcf99b7f8efbf068f24d","tid":206293,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:59:34.000Z","msg":"平凡像我路過<br />\n做乜用2.7 版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a5ffa5e3cfa7bfcb5198603e6cc12dd8f40586","tid":206293,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:34:50.000Z","msg":"目的係 a b c d e -&gt; a b e d c<br />\n即係 0 1 2 3 4 -&gt; 0 1 4 3 2<br />\n我有冇理解錯? 有錯請指正<br />\n<br />\ndef TransformedArray(OriginalArray):<br />\n　　OriginalArray[2], OriginalArray[4] = OriginalArray[4], OriginalArray[2]<br />\n　　return OriginalArray<br />\n<br />\nprint(TransformedArray(['a','b','c','d','e']))<br />\nprint(TransformedArray([1,2,3,4,5]))"}]}